      "topic": "html",
      "sender": "Engineer",
      "content": "<!DOCTYPE html>\n<html lang=\"zh-CN\">\n<head>\n    <meta charset=\"UTF-8\">\n    <meta name=\"viewport\" content=\"width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0\">\n    <title>春节香瓜子葵花子年货促销页</title>\n    <style>\n        :root {\n            --primary-color: #D32F2F;\n            --secondary-color: #FFD700;\n            --bg-light: #F4F4F5;\n        }\n        body {\n            margin: 0;\n            font-family: \"Microsoft YaHei\", sans-serif;\n            background-color: var(--bg-light);\n            color: #333;\n            line-height: 1.6;\n        }\n        header, section, nav, aside, div {\n            padding: 20px;\n            box-sizing: border-box;\n        }\n        .hero {\n            background-color: var(--primary-color);\n            color: #fff;\n            text-align: center;\n            padding: 60px 20px;\n        }\n        .hero h1 {\n            font-size: 2.5rem;\n            margin-bottom: 10px;\n        }\n        .hero p {\n            font-size: 1.2rem;\n        }\n        .product-specs h2 {\n            color: var(--primary-color);\n            margin-bottom: 10px;\n        }\n        .price-box {\n            background-color: #fff;\n            border: 2px solid var(--secondary-color);\n            padding: 15px;\n            margin-top: 20px;\n        }\n        .price-box h3 {\n            margin-bottom: 10px;\n            color: var(--primary-color);\n        }\n        .promotion-tag {\n            display: flex;\n            gap: 10px;\n            margin-top: 10px;\n        }\n        .promotion-tag span {\n            background-color: var(--secondary-color);\n            padding: 5px 10px;\n            border-radius: 4px;\n            font-weight: bold;\n            color: #000;\n        }\n        .countdown-timer {\n            background-color: var(--primary-color);\n            color: #fff;\n            padding: 15px;\n            margin-top: 20px;\n            text-align: center;\n        }\n        .coupon-box {\n            background-color: #fff;\n            padding: 15px;\n            margin-top: 20px;\n            border-left: 5px solid var(--secondary-color);\n        }\n        .purchase-channel {\n            display: flex;\n            gap: 20px;\n            margin-top: 20px;\n        }\n        .purchase-channel button {\n            flex: 1;\n            padding: 15px;\n            border: none;\n            font-size: 1rem;\n            cursor: pointer;\n            border-radius: 4px;\n        }\n        .purchase-channel button:first-child {\n            background-color: var(--secondary-color);\n            color: #000;\n        }\n        .purchase-channel button:last-child {\n            background-color: var(--primary-color);\n            color: #fff;\n        }\n        .cart-overview {\n            background-color: #fff;\n            padding: 15px;\n            margin-top: 20px;\n            border: 1px solid #ddd;\n        }\n        .category-nav {\n            background-color: var(--secondary-color);\n            padding: 15px;\n            margin-top: 20px;\n        }\n        .category-nav h4 {\n            margin-bottom: 10px;\n            color: #000;\n        }\n        .category-nav ul {\n            list-style: none;\n            padding: 0;\n            margin: 0;\n        }\n        .category-nav ul li {\n            margin-bottom: 8px;\n        }\n        .category-nav ul a {\n            color: #000;\n            text-decoration: none;\n        }\n        .reviews {\n            padding: 15px;\n            margin-top: 20px;\n            background-color: #fff;\n            border-top: 5px solid var(--primary-color);\n        }\n        @media (max-width: 768px) {\n            .purchase-channel {\n                flex-direction: column;\n            }\n        }\n    </style>\n</head>\n<body>\n    <section class=\"hero\" id=\"hero\">\n        <h1>热销瓜子·浓浓年味</h1>\n        <p>品牌臻选 | 春节喜庆氛围</p>\n    </section>\n\n    <section class=\"product-specs\" id=\"product-specs\">\n        <h2>产品规格与卖点</h2>\n        <p>精选五谷葵花籽，500克独立包装，富含营养，适合节日聚会与馈赠亲友。</p>\n    </section>\n\n    <div class=\"price-box\" id=\"price-box\">\n        <h3>春节特惠价：￥29.9（原价：￥39.9）</h3>\n        <p>限时折扣，超值享受，物美价廉，送礼佳品。</p>\n    </div>\n\n    <div class=\"promotion-tag\" id=\"promotion-tag\">\n        <span>限时促销</span>\n        <span>库存紧张·热销中</span>\n    </div>\n\n    <div class=\"countdown-timer\" id=\"countdown-timer\">\n        <h3>抢购倒计时</h3>\n        <p>剩余 02:15:36，快行动！</p>\n    </div>\n\n    <section class=\"coupon-box\" id=\"coupon-box\">\n        <h3>电子优惠券</h3>\n        <p>点击领取满100减20优惠券，春节期间均可使用。</p>\n    </section>\n\n    <div class=\"purchase-channel\" id=\"purchase-channel\">\n        <button>加入购物车</button>\n        <button>立即购买</button>\n    </div>\n\n    <aside class=\"cart-overview\" id=\"cart-overview\">\n        <h4>购物车概览</h4>\n        <p>已选商品：春节香瓜子 x 2</p>\n    </aside>\n\n    <nav class=\"category-nav\" id=\"category-nav\">\n        <h4>更多零食分类</h4>\n        <ul>\n            <li><a href=\"#\">坚果系列</a></li>\n            <li><a href=\"#\">糖果巧克力</a></li>\n            <li><a href=\"#\">干果蜜饯</a></li>\n            <li><a href=\"#\">年味糕点</a></li>\n        </ul>\n    </nav>\n\n    <section class=\"reviews\" id=\"reviews\">\n        <h3>用户评价</h3>\n        <p>精选好评，晒出你的美味瞬间，赢取专属礼品。</p>\n    </section>\n</body>\n</html>"
    }
